ember_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Hi,\n\nDuring registration of account at https://tams.preprod.gsa.gov, e-mail verification (code validation) can be bypassed through intercepting \u0026 modifying the response status-from \"success\":false to \"success\":true\nVideo {F1284281} is for reference.\n\n##Steps To Reproduce\n1. Open User Registration  Url - https://tams.preprod.gsa.gov/userEmailReg\n2. Enter the email \u0026 submit.\n3. Prompt to enter the verification code will appear.\n4. Enter any wrong value (6 digits), submit \u0026 capture in burp.\n5.Before submitting, select the option in burp - Do Intercept response to this request\n6. After receiving the response. Modify the value false to true for success parameter.\n7. You would be able to continue the registration process. \n8. A pop up appears in the next stage. You can close \u0026 go ahead with registration process.\n\n## Impact\n\nBypass of e-mail verification processes.","weakness":{"id":57,"name":"Violation of Secure Design Principles"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":1284281,"file_name":"recording-1619794572349.webm","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/6km2fum84v8hdnoz4d27803echpn?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22recording-1619794572349.webm%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27recording-1619794572349.webm\u0026response-content-type=video%2Fwebm\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQ3AQIHSJL%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T081141Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIBb%2F7ajla8vtEKoWQOIpLCccIvnPW3hcPCb%2FNQRXSZaLAiAxBKUHPk76EJW3ju%2FZ2lhF01Uag6xiXOhG0wxT5DyRuyq7BQjx%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMfhI%2BSplPc0JRr%2FSpKo8FWPsymTitguN%2BJ